<br />

<br />
With the entire camp, the 1st pet you have is down to 10% in around 15 seconds. Its wonderful tearing through most of the camp. I can take down an entire camp (depending on resists/chanting time) in 15minutes.
<br />

<br />
I was freaked out by PoN Stalkers at first, but hit F9 4 times then just ran past a few or all of them. I ran around the fake treant to gather them up, then would charm one stick it on another stalker and run like an idiot around my pet (at a safe distance) until my pet got aggro.
<br />

<br />
Once my pet got aggro I wait till its time to break charm with invis. Once I break charm I run towards the entrance of PoN. Not very far, just a small grouping of trees near the false treant. Chant it down, let it die. Con the corpse, if I got 7mins I run towards stalker camp and sit on edge of pit farthest from zone in and wait for my doggies to get near, double tap F9 into first person and run to loot corpse. I've only died 3 times so far. If thats confusing I'll make a better guide with pictures if you want.</span></td>
